                     <interp inst="t18281204-134-off707" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18281204-134-cd708" type="crimeDate">15th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-134-off707 t18281204-134-cd708"></join>, 10 pairs of shoes, value 20s.
            </rs>, the goods of the 
